------------------------------------------------------------------------

This is a faithful port of SQLite 3 (https://sqlite.org/) from C to
Free Pascal.  The original SQLite C source code is in the public domain,
authored by D. Richard Hipp and contributors.  This Pascal port adopts
the same public-domain posture.

The C reference source (../sqlite3/) is copyright its respective authors
and also public domain, per the SQLite project's own licensing terms at:
  https://sqlite.org/copyright.html
